OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,FThe wife of a Cumbrian police officer
OL,7,Fwho took his own life has told an
OL,8,Finquest into his death that 'he was
OL,9,Flet down by the job he loved'.
OL,11,FJennifer Thistlethwaite described her
OL,12,Fhusband James as her "soulmate of 27
OL,13,Fyears," and told Workington Coroner's
OL,14,FCourt that his role as a police
OL,15,Fofficer caused his PTSD.
OL,17,FMr Thistlethwaite was found dead at
OL,18,Fhis home in Keswick in August 2023.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
