CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780665076
OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,FShe referred to an incident he
OL,7,Fattended in October 2021 involving a
OL,8,Fbaby's death, stating it had a life
OL,9,Fchanging effect on him.
OL,11,FMrs Thistlethwaite told the inquest
OL,12,FJames became distant and couldn't stop
OL,13,Fthinking about the child.
OL,15,FShe said another incident soon after
OL,16,Finvolving a man's death on a mountain
OL,17,Fcaused him to withdraw further and
OL,18,Fbecome "a shell", and said years
OL,19,Fbefore he had also been at the scene
OL,20,Fof the fatal Keswick school bus crash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780665076
OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,FMrs Thistlethwaite told the hearing he
OL,7,Fhad been having suicidal thoughts for
OL,8,Fup to a year and was receiving mental
OL,9,Fhealth support from Cumbria,
OL,10,FNorthumberland, Tyne and Wear NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust.
OL,13,FShe said Cumbria Police as an
OL,14,Forganisation did not offer him
OL,15,Fappropriate support for his PTSD,
OL,16,Falthough individuals within police did
OL,17,Fhelp him.
OL,19,FA former police colleague told the
OL,20,Fcourt there was a "stiff upper lip
OL,21,Fapproach."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780665076
OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,FThe ininquest heard that at the time
OL,7,Fof his death, Cumbria Police were
OL,8,Finvestigating him over allegations of
OL,9,Fsexual offences against a woman
OL,10,Freferred to as Miss X.
OL,12,FMrs Thistlethwaite said NHS failings
OL,13,Fand the prolonged police investigation
OL,14,Finto misconduct claims contributed to
OL,15,Fher husband's death.
OL,17,FIn a statement, she described James as
OL,18,F"a deeply loved husband, father, son,
OL,19,Fbrother, uncle and friend whose
OL,20,Fwarmth, kindness, and spirit touched
OL,21,Fthe lives of everyone who knew him."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780665076
OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,FShe said: "While we now have the
OL,7,Fcoroner's formal findings regarding
OL,8,FJames's tragic passing by suicide,
OL,9,Funderstanding them does not make the
OL,10,Freality of his absence any easier to
OL,11,Fbear.
OL,13,F"We kindly and urgently ask the media
OL,14,Fand the public to grant us the space,
OL,15,Ftime, and privacy we need to process
OL,16,Fthese findings and to grieve together
OL,17,Fas a family.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
