PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780665076
OL,3,CPolice officer was 'let down by the
OL,4,Cjob he loved' before suicide, says wife
OL,6,F"We need this time to support one
OL,7,Fanother and to focus on honouring
OL,8,FJames's memory away from the public
OL,9,Feye."
OL,11,FThe inquest continues.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
